### Create account
POST http://localhost:3300/account
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ownerName": "John"
}

### Use the ids you get after creating account to verify the endpoints
### Get account by id
GET http://localhost:3300/account/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### Get account transactions
GET http://localhost:3300/account/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/transactions

### Deposit
POST http://localhost:3300/account/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/deposit
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 100.00,
  "note": "Initial deposit"
}

### Withdraw
POST http://localhost:3300/account/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/withdraw
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 25.00,
  "note": "ATM withdrawal"
}

### Transfer
POST http://localhost:3300/transfer
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "fromAccountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000",
  "toAccountId": "00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001",
  "amount": 50.00,
  "note": "Rent"
}